OL,4,G1900FAbandoned Engineering
OL,5,     GExtraordinary abandoned relics of
OL,6,     Gcommunist rule are uncovered,
OL,7,     Gincluding the former Soviet Army
OL,8,     GHQ in East Germany and Tito's
OL,9,     Ghidden Cold War submarine base on
OL,10,     Gthe island of Vis.
OL,11,G2000FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,12,     GIn 1944, U.S. forces fought a
OL,13,     Gbrutal battle to seize a coral
OL,14,     Gisland in the Kwajalein Atoll
OL,15,     Gfrom entrenched Japanese troops,
OL,16,     Gsecuring a vital South Pacific
OL,17,     Gmilitary base.
