OL,4,G2030FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,5,     GAs the United States prepared for
OL,6,     Gthe invasion of the Philippines,
OL,7,     Gscheduled for late 1944, the tiny
OL,8,     GPalau Islands had to be taken
OL,9,     Gfirst.
OL,10,G2100FHow the Nazis Lost the War
OL,11,     GGermany had few allies before
OL,12,     GWWII, and, for various reasons,
OL,13,     Gthose alliances were doomed to
OL,14,     Gfail. Ultimately, Germany paid a
OL,15,     Gheavy price for the partnerships
OL,16,     Gthey forged with the Axis Powers.
